description:
Men's Fitness June 2013 (USA)
English | 170 pages | PDF | 104.40 MB




Men's Fitness is for men, who want to get more 
out of their lives and celebrates an upbeat, optimistic, 
pro-active lifestyle. Men's Fitness recognizes, that mental 
and emotional fitness is vital to balanced living and aims 
to offer active and aspirational men - entertainment, 
information and inspiration.
